name: Homepage HTTP Status Code Should Be STATUS_OK (200)
fullName: Test Cases.Check All Urls.Homepage HTTP Status Code Should Be STATUS_OK (200)
description:
This test checks whether the JLT homepage returns an HTTP status code of 200 (OK).
Steps:
1. Check if Homepage is visible
2. Send a GET request to the JLT homepage.
3. Verify that the received HTTP status code is 200.
